elements.name: Test production IBM GUI flow for AP

steps.name: Click on Prod Rewrite GUI link
GUI home page should open
Click on SelectARole dropdown and select TROOPPRV1-AP OO on profit plan (V1-Dummy-Singapore)
Click on Start button
Home page should open
Click on Create quote button
New quote page should open for prod rw AP
Enter QuoteTitle OppID OppOwnerName for AP /LA
Click on Save and Continue
On Customer information page click on Add a new Customer
Enter customer name
Click on Save and Continue on customer tab
Add product manually
click on collect pricing
Click on Save and Continue on Configuration tab
Click on Request Approval and send the quote for approval
Verify the status of the quote
close the window
Click on Prod Rewrite GUI link
GUI home page should open
Click on SelectARole dropdown and select TRPRV1-AP Pricer (V1-Dummy-Singapore)
Click on Start button
Search for the quoteID from excel sheet for AP prod rw
Click on Reviwer tab and add a reviwer
Click on pricing tab
Approve the quote using Approval tab for AP

steps.name: Enter all the details to rediect to IBM PCS page
GUI home page should open
Click on SelectARole dropdown and select SP1 Maint - COV TR X1
Click on Start button
Home page should open
Click on Create quote button
In Overview tab enter the required details_SB
Click on Save and Continue
Add product manually for PCS
click on collect pricing for PCS
fill details inside Registration and customer tab for PCS
in Details pricing tab click on Submit price request
inside submit and send popup enter email id and send email
close the window
Click on Prod Rewrite GUI link
GUI home page should open
Click on SelectARole dropdown and select X1 Channel Pricer
Click on Start button
Search for the quoteID from excel sheet for PCS NA BP prod rw
Click on comments and status and remove the quote from on hold status
Click on pricing tab and approve the quote
verify reports for BP
